    Created by  : Bambang Hariyanto,Ir.,MT.
    Date        : March 1, 2002
    Description : Thermometer Class
		  Invalid value handling, without Structured Exception Handling
    ===========================================================================    
    Compiling & execution Instructions:         
	prompt\> javac ThermometerApp         
	prompt\> java ThermometerApp    
    ===========================================================================    
    Approved by  : 
    Tested by    :
